data.description: This is a stunning and well-designed 1-story 4 sides masonry home with a variety of attractive features and amenities located in Bandera River Ranch. This is a true 3 bedroom, 2 bath with a formal dining room  and it is as beautiful as it is functional! The open floor plan, hard surface flooring, and vaulted ceilings contribute to a bright and spacious interior. kitchen is a focal point, boasting granite countertops, stainless appliances generously sized kitchen island that serves both as a workspace and a breakfast bar. The primary bedroom is quite luxurious, with its en-suite bathroom offering a walk-in shower, garden tub, double vanities, and a walk-in closet with built-in shelving. This provides ample storage and a private retreat within the home. The arrangement of the remaining bedrooms and separate bathroom adds a level of privacy and convenience. Moving outdoors, the covered patio enhances the outdoor living space, making it suitable for relaxation and entertaining. The large, lush back yard with a privacy fence and covered RV Storage with hook up is a wonderful feature for those who appreciate outdoor beauty and hill country views. Bandera River Ranch offers a river park, pool, sports courts and playground adds value for those who enjoy outdoor activities.
